<Layout title="RV Rentals • Interstate Cupcakes">
  <h2>Festival-first rigs that don’t crumble on Day 2.</h2>
  <p>Comfort, reliability, and a setup designed for festivals and road trips.</p>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Cupcake-One — Class C (24’)</h3>
      <ul class="check">
        <li>Sleeps 4–6 • cold A/C • solar assist • inverter</li>
        <li>Outdoor rug + shade setup • cooler mount • LED camp lights</li>
        <li>Add‑ons: generator • projector • water refill • cleanup kit</li>
      </ul>
      <p><a class="button" href="/contact">Request availability →</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Cupcake-Two — Travel Trailer (20’)</h3>
      <ul class="check">
        <li>Lightweight tow • sleeps 3–4 • festival pack included</li>
        <li>Blackout shades • fans • USB-everywhere</li>
        <li>Add‑ons: hitch kit • stabilizers • extra batteries</li>
      </ul>
      <p><a class="button" href="/contact">Request availability →</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Festival checklist</h2>
  <ul class="check">
    <li>Power</li><li>Shade</li><li>Cooling</li><li>Water</li><li>Sleep</li><li>Cleanup</li><li>Exit plan</li>
  </ul>
  <p><small class="muted">We’ll send you a pack list that saves your weekend.</small></p>
</Layout>
